response.overview: In 1989, a misunderstood teenager has a high school crush — who just happens to be a handsome corpse! After a set of playfully horrific circumstances bring him back to life, the two embark on a murderous journey to find love, happiness…and a few missing body parts along the way.
response.tagline: If you can't meet your perfect boyfriend…make him.
response.title: Lisa Frankenstein
